      • setPropertiesFromMap

        public static void setPropertiesFromMap(Map<String,String> map)
        循环 map ,设置到系统属性 System.setProperty(String, String).

        如果 map 是null,抛出 NullPointerException
        如果 map 是empty,抛出 IllegalArgumentException

        Parameters:
        map - the properties from map
        Since:
        1.2.0
        See Also:
        System.setProperty(String, String)
